#BoredApeDonutShop #BADS #runningoutoflove #BAYC #ALEXA

Running Out of Love (feat.AleXa) out now : https://ADA.lnk.to/BADSROOL

In the heart of a desolate desert, the Bored Ape Donut Shop (BADS) used to be a beacon of hope, where travelers from all walks of life came to quench their thirst and fill their bellies. To the three Bored Ape brothers - ILLA (BAYC#4419), INGU (BAYC#4401), and NUTS (MAYC#9225) - this place means more than just a pit stop on the highway. Here, in the sweltering heat of the donut shop, they poured their souls into the music, dreaming of the day when they would become super producers and take the music scene by storm. And unexpectedly their dreams became a reality when the legendary musician FENNY stumbled upon their humble shop. Collaborating with the superstar, the BADS brothers produced "Running Out of Love" in hopes to change their lives forever.
